name: Classfinder
tagline: Java library and stand-alone Swing application that helps in finding individual resources in a predefined classpath
body:
### Java library
ClassFinder is a java library with the API documented in https://jorgeb1980.github.io/ClassFinder/mvn-site/apidocs

### Independent app
ClassFinder behaves as an independent app

    java -jar Classfinder.jar
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
